Package biscotti.collections

This package contains interfaces, implementations, and other utilities for working with Collections.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BoundedMap<K,V> A capacity restricted Map.
BoundedQueue<E> A capacity restricted Queue.
 

Class Summary
Collections3 Static methods which operate on or return Collections.
FIFOMap<K,V> A LinkedHashMap implementation of BoundedMap which removes stale mappings in insertion/first-in-first-out (FIFO) order.
ForwardingDeque<E> A Deque which forwards all its method calls to another Deque.
ForwardingNavigableSet<E> A NavigableSet which forwards all its method calls to another NavigableSet.
ForwardingPeekingIterator<E> A PeekingIterator which forwards all its method calls to another PeekingIterator.
Iterables2 Static methods which operate on or return Iterables.
Iterators2 Static methods which operate on or return Iterators.
LinkedBoundedQueue<E> A linked list implementation of BoundedQueue.
LRUMap<K,V> A LinkedHashMap implementation of BoundedMap which removes stale mappings in access/least-recently-used (LRU) order.
Maps2 Static methods which operate on or return Maps.
PriorityBoundedQueue<E> An implementation of BoundedQueue backed by a PriorityQueue.
PriorityDeque<E> An unbounded priority Deque based on a modified red-black tree.
PriorityQueue<E> An unbounded priority Queue based on a modified red-black tree.
Sets2 Static methods which operate on or return Sets.
SortedList<E> A sorted List based on a modified red-black tree.
UnmodifiableListIterator<E> A ListIterator that does not support remove(), add(), and set(E).
UnmodifiablePeekingIterator<E> A PeekingIterator that does not support remove().
 

Package biscotti.collections Description

This package contains interfaces, implementations, and other utilities for working with Collections.
